<div class="table">
    <h2>How to make a Table</h2>
    <table border="1"> 
        <caption><code><span class="keyword">caption</span> tag for table caption</code></caption>
        <thead><code>
            <ul><li><span class="keyword">thead</span> is TABLE HEAD, and is used to group header content, in an HTML table.</li>
            <ul><li>basically table version of <code><span class="keyword">header</span></code></li></ul><br>
            <li><span class="keyword">tbody</span> is TABLE BODY, and is used to group the body content, aka table data, in an HTML table</li>
            <ul><li>basically table version of <code><span class="keyword">body</span></code></li></ul><br>
            <li><span class="keyword">TD</span> is TABLE DATA and is the vertical boxes in a table</li>
            <ul><li>basically table version of <code><span class="keyword">body</span></code></li></ul><br>
            <li><span class="keyword">TH</span> is TABLE HEADER and is the horizontal boxes in a table</li>
            <ul><li>basically table version of <code><span class="keyword">body</span></code></li></ul><br>
            <li><span class="keyword">TR</span> is TABLE ROW and is the horizontal section in a table</li>
            <ul><li>basically table version of <code><span class="keyword">body</span></code></li></ul><br></ul>
        </code></div>
        

    <tr align="center"><h3>TR makes a table row</h3>
        <th width="100">TH Examples</th>
        <th width="100">TH Examples</th>
        <th width="100">TH Examples</th>
        <th width="100">TH Examples</th>
        <th width="290">This whole left-to-right (horizontal) section is a TR, or Table Row</th>

        </thead>
        </tr>
        
        <tbody>
    <tr align="center">
        <td>TD is table data</td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td> </tbody>
    </tr>
    
    <tr align="center">
        <td>Use another TR tag to make more rows</td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
        <td></td>
    </tr>
    </table>
